title: The FoodSaver® FM1510 Fresh Food Preservation System - Zipper Bags
description: The FoodSaver Fresh Food Preservation System seals in freshness of foods stored in the fridge, pantry and on the go. Easily and conveniently vacuum seal FoodSaver Fresh Containers and Vacuum Zipper Bags for storage of everyday foods, leftovers and prep-ahead ingredients. Its compact design is made for everyday countertop use and its one-touch sealing allows for hand-free operation once the sealing process starts.

transcripts: It's easy to extend the freshness of your food with the FoodSaver fresh food preservation system and its specially designed to work with your food saver zipper bags. Now with the innovative FoodSaver fresh appliance there's a better way to organize store and keep your food fresh up to two times longer begin by placing food into zipper bag making sure not to overfill firmly press the length of the zipper seal with your fingers to ensure it is closed. Align the zipper bag valve with the crosshairs located at the base. Press the buttons to adjust the height of the vacuum head, firmly press nozzle against zipper bag accessport the ready light lets you know it's ready to seal just press start and it does the rest. Whether you're storing fruits and veggies deli meats, baked good, or cheese there's a FoodSaver zipper bag for all your precious ingredients. The vacuum process stops automatically when freshness sealed in, perfect for storing your favorite foods in the fridge or the pantry. Trust your food freshness to the new foodsaver fresh food preservation system.
